Package ariba.ui.widgets Description

Primary library of UI controls for AribaWeb, ranging from buttons, choosers, and popup menus, to tab controls, and portlet boxes, as well as full page wrappers.

w: namespace -- Namespace aware templates typically refer to these components with the "w:" prefix (e.g.<w:TextButton/>)

Commonly used components include:

  • Page Wrappers:
    • w:BasicPageWrapper
    • w:ModalPageWrapper
  • Controls:
    • w:TextButton
    • w:PopupMenuLink, w:PulldownButton w:PopupMenu, w:PopupMenuItem
    • w:DateField
    • w:Chooser
  • Help:
    • w:HintMessage
    • w:CueTip
    • w:ErrorFlag
  • Layout:
    • w:TabSet, w:Tab
    • w:SectionHeading, w:SectionBody
    • w:OutlineBox, w:PortletWrapper

Several other packages provide additional groups of controls:

See Also:
ariba.ui.table, ariba.ui.outline, ariba.ui.validation
